Evergrande Real Estate Buys 111 Million Shares on July 19

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-07-20T02:47:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/evergrande-real-estate-buys-111-million-shares-on-july-19-1-.html
Evergrande Real Estate Group Ltd. (3333) 
bought 111 million shares of the company for HK$656 million ($84
million) on July 19, according to a statement to the Hong Kong
stock exchange late yesterday.  The stock fell 1.7 percent to HK$5.92 as of 10:42 a.m.
after climbing 7.3 percent yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marco Lui in Hong Kong at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
